VALUES
(2947901, 'The omens are clear, traveler. The eyes and tear of the Earthmother still bless our skies during the eternal cycle of night and day. And yet, they have grown distant from each other, much like our people. A time has come when sibling will fight sibling, when the very blood that unites us will be shed across the blue grass of our coast. It is a heavy cost and an even heavier burden. A future we need not know, but will.', 'The omens are clear, traveler. The eyes and tear of the Earthmother still bless our skies during the eternal cycle of night and day. And yet, they have grown distant from each other, much like our people. A time has come when sibling will fight sibling, when the very blood that unites us will be shed across the blue grass of our coast. It is a heavy cost and an even heavier burden. A future we need not know, but will.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6214101, 'Come see my wares! I''ve imported them straight from beyond the Great Sea!', 'Come see my wares! I''ve imported them straight from beyond the Great Sea!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6214201, 'This heat is killing me! What I would give for an ice cold mug of Amberale.', 'This heat is killing me! What I would give for an ice cold mug of Amberale.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6214301, 'My good-for-nothing son is daydreaming about becoming a knight and courting his woman all day long. If only he used that energy to inherit my craft...', 'My good-for-nothing son is daydreaming about becoming a knight and courting his woman all day long. If only he used that energy to inherit my craft...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6214401, 'The best way to get good at fishing is becoming old. No fish gets scared if you can''t even move that much anymore, ha!', 'The best way to get good at fishing is becoming old. No fish gets scared if you can''t even move that much anymore, ha!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6214501, 'I wish to browse your wares, Calandrath.', 'I wish to browse your wares, Calandrath.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6214502, 'Welcome to the Honey Drop Inn! Grab a seat and enjoy Northwind''s finest cuisine!', 'Welcome to the Honey Drop Inn! Grab a seat and enjoy Northwind''s finest cuisine!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6214601, 'Miss Ellerian sent me to grab bundle of apples.', 'Miss Ellerian sent me to grab bundle of apples.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6214602, 'Greetings! Anything you need for your stay? We still have some empty beds left, so we would love to have you stay overnight!', 'Greetings! Anything you need for your stay? We still have some empty beds left, so we would love to have you stay overnight!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6214603, 'Here you go, I had these saved just for her.', 'Here you go, I had these saved just for her.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6214701, 'Anywhere my sturdy gryphons can take you?', 'Anywhere my sturdy gryphons can take you?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215001, 'Have you paid your respects to Queen Tiffin yet? If not, why not purchase one of my bouquets and offer it just over there in Tiffin Park?', 'Have you paid your respects to Queen Tiffin yet? If not, why not purchase one of my bouquets and offer it just over there in Tiffin Park?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215101, 'Only the finest flour is used to make these marvelous treats!', 'Only the finest flour is used to make these marvelous treats!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215201, 'You won''t find any finer wares in all of Stormwind; only the mastersmiths of Ironforge can hold a candle to my weaponry!', 'You won''t find any finer wares in all of Stormwind; only the mastersmiths of Ironforge can hold a candle to my weaponry!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215301, 'I am here on behalf of SI:7 Operative Hawthorne. Have you noticed anything suspicious during the previous nights?', 'I am here on behalf of SI:7 Operative Hawthorne. Have you noticed anything suspicious during the previous nights?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215302, 'What do you want from me? I really have neither the time nor the luster to bother myself with the insignificant squabbles of an adventurer.', 'What do you want from me? I really have neither the time nor the luster to bother myself with the insignificant squabbles of an adventurer.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215303, 'So you''re Hawthorne''s dog, I take it?  With each passing day, the kingdom draws closer to ruin. That Stormwind is sending just one measly person to solve all our problems is all we need as proof. To answer your question: Yes, I have noticed ‘suspicious activity'' the past few days. Blackrock Orcs have invaded our vale, razing the entirety of Birkhaven to the ground and locking themselves in a stalemate with the Dark Iron that ALSO invaded Northwind. It is to be expected for people to disappear under these circumstances.', 'So you''re Hawthorne''s dog, I take it?  With each passing day, the kingdom draws closer to ruin. That Stormwind is sending just one measly person to solve all our problems is all we need as proof. To answer your question: Yes, I have noticed ‘suspicious activity'' the past few days. Blackrock Orcs have invaded our vale, razing the entirety of Birkhaven to the ground and locking themselves in a stalemate with the Dark Iron that ALSO invaded Northwind. It is to be expected for people to disappear under these circumstances.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215304, 'Bailiff Lancaster, Lord Amberwood sends me to get your report for Lady Prestor.', 'Bailiff Lancaster, Lord Amberwood sends me to get your report for Lady Prestor.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215401, 'I am here on behalf of SI:7 Operative Hawthorne. Have you noticed anything suspicious during the previous nights?', 'I am here on behalf of SI:7 Operative Hawthorne. Have you noticed anything suspicious during the previous nights?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215402, 'These leaves just never stop falling.', 'These leaves just never stop falling.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215403, 'I must tell you, I rarely go out during the night nowadays. It''s not as safe as it used to be around town anymore, especially for an old man like myself. Dubious characters skulk around the park and outskirts of town, it is harrowing. My heart aches for those who disappeared, the people of Northwind are sincere and just. They do not deserve all the tragedy.', 'I must tell you, I rarely go out during the night nowadays. It''s not as safe as it used to be around town anymore, especially for an old man like myself. Dubious characters skulk around the park and outskirts of town, it is harrowing. My heart aches for those who disappeared, the people of Northwind are sincere and just. They do not deserve all the tragedy.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215501, 'Dark times are ahead, adventurer. Much of the peace and tranquility that is left in Northwind vanishes with each passing hour. These lands are falling apart and no one seems to care about it. Neither his Lordship nor the King. It falls to me - to the people - to salvage this tragedy that befalls us. Missing people, invading Defias, Blackrocks and Dark Irons, Gnolls running amok, the whole town of Birkhaven in ruins. I have my hands full of problems and none left to grasp at solutions. I implore on your good faith and morals: Please, help the people of Northwind.', 'Dark times are ahead, adventurer. Much of the peace and tranquility that is left in Northwind vanishes with each passing hour. These lands are falling apart and no one seems to care about it. Neither his Lordship nor the King. It falls to me - to the people - to salvage this tragedy that befalls us. Missing people, invading Defias, Blackrocks and Dark Irons, Gnolls running amok, the whole town of Birkhaven in ruins. I have my hands full of problems and none left to grasp at solutions. I implore on your good faith and morals: Please, help the people of Northwind.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215601, 'Have you heard the tale of Sir Edrin Vellas? A simple peasant who became one of Stormwind''s greatest knights. He is a local legend, there isn''t anyone who doesn''t know his name and deeds. I wish I could one day become like him - a true knight, traveling the world, seeking adventure and protecting the innocent!', 'Have you heard the tale of Sir Edrin Vellas? A simple peasant who became one of Stormwind''s greatest knights. He is a local legend, there isn''t anyone who doesn''t know his name and deeds. I wish I could one day become like him - a true knight, traveling the world, seeking adventure and protecting the innocent!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215701, 'Henry is such a charmer. He took me out for dinner here at the Plump Pumpkin even though he is knee-deep in becoming a blacksmith like his father. I appreciate him taking time out of his day for me; his father doesn''t mind us two meeting, but he''d prefer if Henry spent more time at the forge.$B$B<Theresa chuckles.>$B$BMartin really tries his best, but I doubt he''ll be able to reign in his son''s adventurous spirit. Not even I can do that.', 'Henry is such a charmer. He took me out for dinner here at the Plump Pumpkin even though he is knee-deep in becoming a blacksmith like his father. I appreciate him taking time out of his day for me; his father doesn''t mind us two meeting, but he''d prefer if Henry spent more time at the forge.$B$B<Theresa chuckles.>$B$BMartin really tries his best, but I doubt he''ll be able to reign in his son''s adventurous spirit. Not even I can do that.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215801, 'What a commotion. The Plump Pumpkin is usually bustling with visitors, but with all the invaders from the east all I got is this brooding relic over there asking me too many questions. Either way; welcome to the Plump Pumpkin! Hungry or thirsty, by chance?', 'What a commotion. The Plump Pumpkin is usually bustling with visitors, but with all the invaders from the east all I got is this brooding relic over there asking me too many questions. Either way; welcome to the Plump Pumpkin! Hungry or thirsty, by chance?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6215901, 'Mister Thorpe has had a very busy day, so don''t hesitate to ask me to pass you any of our delicious drinks!', 'Mister Thorpe has had a very busy day, so don''t hesitate to ask me to pass you any of our delicious drinks!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216201, 'Accursed low-lifes! I will not stand for such exorbitance in my lands. The moment this farce of a tournament is over, I will execute swift judgement upon them!', 'Accursed low-lifes! I will not stand for such exorbitance in my lands. The moment this farce of a tournament is over, I will execute swift judgement upon them!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216301, 'Good lady, just what chaos has befallen these lands?', 'Good lady, just what chaos has befallen these lands?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216302, 'King''s Honor, friend. Please make sure you behave accordingly when walking these halls. We really can''t afford any more trouble than we already have.', 'King''s Honor, friend. Please make sure you behave accordingly when walking these halls. We really can''t afford any more trouble than we already have.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216303, 'Simply too much. Lord Amberwood has fortified this land formidibly before, yet with most of his troops delegated back to Stormwind, our beloved Northwind laid bare for the taking. All we can protect now are the southern forests of Northwind, and even then we''re hardly scraping by. I am simply relieved to see my nephew safe and sound within the castle walls. I promised his late mother, my darling sister, to never have any harm befall him. And I intend to uphold that promise with all the power that I have.', 'Simply too much. Lord Amberwood has fortified this land formidibly before, yet with most of his troops delegated back to Stormwind, our beloved Northwind laid bare for the taking. All we can protect now are the southern forests of Northwind, and even then we''re hardly scraping by. I am simply relieved to see my nephew safe and sound within the castle walls. I promised his late mother, my darling sister, to never have any harm befall him. And I intend to uphold that promise with all the power that I have.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216401, 'Sir Amberwood, your brother asked me to deliver your report to Lady Katrana Prestor.', 'Sir Amberwood, your brother asked me to deliver your report to Lady Katrana Prestor.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216402, 'Don''t test my patience, peasant. I am not as complacent as my brother.', 'Don''t test my patience, peasant. I am not as complacent as my brother.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216403, 'Did my brother run out of messengers? Regrettable. You can see what sorry state Northwind has become, a shame you have to witness this. No matter, it is the duty of us nobles to sort this chaos out. Here, take this scroll to Lady Prestor. I am certain she will appreciate it.', 'Did my brother run out of messengers? Regrettable. You can see what sorry state Northwind has become, a shame you have to witness this. No matter, it is the duty of us nobles to sort this chaos out. Here, take this scroll to Lady Prestor. I am certain she will appreciate it.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6216501, 'Welcome to Northwind. I apologize for the sorry state you find it in. It seems all of these problems come crashing down on me all at once. And on top of it I don''t even have enough soldiers to sufficiently protect my subjects. The populace may think neither I nor my brother care all that much, but that couldn''t be further from the truth. And yet, all the strength I have left to solve this chaos is bound by the orders of my king.', 'Welcome to Northwind. I apologize for the sorry state you find it in. It seems all of these problems come crashing down on me all at once. And on top of it I don''t even have enough soldiers to sufficiently protect my subjects. The populace may think neither I nor my brother care all that much, but that couldn''t be further from the truth. And yet, all the strength I have left to solve this chaos is bound by the orders of my king.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6218301, 'My family has been serving the Mildenhalls for many generations. Our professionally cared for horses possess a prime physique and extraordinary speed as well as the stamina matching such skills. If you have the coin, I could teach you how horses are ridden here in Northwind.', 'My family has been serving the Mildenhalls for many generations. Our professionally cared for horses possess a prime physique and extraordinary speed as well as the stamina matching such skills. If you have the coin, I could teach you how horses are ridden here in Northwind.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6218401, 'My husband and I have our hands tied with caring for the jousting horse just yonder the road. Many of them require special treatment and feed, and with only Jorg as extra help, it can get quite busy around here. Nevertheless, take a look at our other horses here; they are the best steeds in the entire kingdom! Lady Mildenhall''s horses are famous among the most prestigious knights and nobles of the capital.', 'My husband and I have our hands tied with caring for the jousting horse just yonder the road. Many of them require special treatment and feed, and with only Jorg as extra help, it can get quite busy around here. Nevertheless, take a look at our other horses here; they are the best steeds in the entire kingdom! Lady Mildenhall''s horses are famous among the most prestigious knights and nobles of the capital.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6218402, 'I would like to buy from you.', 'I would like to buy from you.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6218501, 'This is not how I imagined my vacation. The Geringts needed the workforce because of the tournament, and with no one else here, it''s only me cleaning the stables at the moment. To be completely honest with you... I don''t feel particularly safe on my own here. Mr. Geringt has me cover the last shift here and with all the rumours going around about people being abducted and what not, I''d rather hole up at my house and not come out!', 'This is not how I imagined my vacation. The Geringts needed the workforce because of the tournament, and with no one else here, it''s only me cleaning the stables at the moment. To be completely honest with you... I don''t feel particularly safe on my own here. Mr. Geringt has me cover the last shift here and with all the rumours going around about people being abducted and what not, I''d rather hole up at my house and not come out!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6218601, 'Come here and grab a box of scrumptious Amberglaze Donuts, made from local Ambersap! Get them now while they are still crispy and warm!', 'Come here and grab a box of scrumptious Amberglaze Donuts, made from local Ambersap! Get them now while they are still crispy and warm!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6218701, 'Don''t get distracted by this loudmouth next to me; what you need is an ice cold beverage to keep you hydrated while admiring the contestant''s sportsmanship!', 'Don''t get distracted by this loudmouth next to me; what you need is an ice cold beverage to keep you hydrated while admiring the contestant''s sportsmanship!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6219701, 'The air is resonating with resentment. Whatever has angered the lords of air, it does not bode well.', 'The air is resonating with resentment. Whatever has angered the lords of air, it does not bode well.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6219801, 'Da spirit be whispering about a great unrest. De elements are weeping and we be seeing de result of it.', 'Da spirit be whispering about a great unrest. De elements are weeping and we be seeing de result of it.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6227501, 'I''m not really cut out for this military stuff, but if there''s a way for me to protect my home, then I will do whatever it takes.', 'I''m not really cut out for this military stuff, but if there''s a way for me to protect my home, then I will do whatever it takes.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6227601, 'There is something foul within Northwind. A sickness within, how small it may be at first, can quickly germinate and infect. We cannot let that happen.', 'There is something foul within Northwind. A sickness within, how small it may be at first, can quickly germinate and infect. We cannot let that happen.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6227701, 'Lion''s Watch used to be heavily guarded as part of the Merchant''s Highroad, but nowadays only us militia folk are sticking around. Makes you think what the nobility is up to.', 'Lion''s Watch used to be heavily guarded as part of the Merchant''s Highroad, but nowadays only us militia folk are sticking around. Makes you think what the nobility is up to.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6227801, 'In all my years as a merchant have I seen such a disaster. A shameful display for Stormwind.', 'In all my years as a merchant have I seen such a disaster. A shameful display for Stormwind.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6227901, 'Mourning is something all people have in common. No matter how young or old we are, we all end up mourning our dead. Whether they were taken from us too soon or not, it matters little. Our hearts simply cannot bear the ache. I never imagined I would outlive my own daughter—yet here I am, staring at a statue that barely resembles her.$B$BMy Tiffin was no warrior, but she was a kind, tender soul. Some still remember their short-lived queen and come to pay their respects. For that, I am grateful and content. I long to see her face again, her silly smile, her golden hair.$B$B<Ingvild tears up.>$B$BAnd I could still see her, if only they would allow me entry into Stormwind. I could see my Tiffin in the face of my grandchild, whom I long to see every day. Yet they deny me. That poor boy, alone in the world, with a dead mother and a missing father. If only he knew how much I love him.', 'Mourning is something all people have in common. No matter how young or old we are, we all end up mourning our dead. Whether they were taken from us too soon or not, it matters little. Our hearts simply cannot bear the ache. I never imagined I would outlive my own daughter—yet here I am, staring at a statue that barely resembles her.$B$BMy Tiffin was no warrior, but she was a kind, tender soul. Some still remember their short-lived queen and come to pay their respects. For that, I am grateful and content. I long to see her face again, her silly smile, her golden hair.$B$B<Ingvild tears up.>$B$BAnd I could still see her, if only they would allow me entry into Stormwind. I could see my Tiffin in the face of my grandchild, whom I long to see every day. Yet they deny me. That poor boy, alone in the world, with a dead mother and a missing father. If only he knew how much I love him.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6228001, 'Please stay quiet while you visit the church and respect the departed''s eternal rest.', 'Please stay quiet while you visit the church and respect the departed''s eternal rest.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6228301, 'So much to do, so little time. Please, don''t make a mess while you are here!', 'So much to do, so little time. Please, don''t make a mess while you are here!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6228501, 'Watch your manners and respect the queue. Cutting in line won''t get you a quicker audience with Lord Amberwood!', 'Watch your manners and respect the queue. Cutting in line won''t get you a quicker audience with Lord Amberwood!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6228601, 'Oh my, a visitor...! Please be quiet around here and don''t disturb the flowers...', 'Oh my, a visitor...! Please be quiet around here and don''t disturb the flowers...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6228801, 'Can you feel the essence of this vale? The crimson trees, rolling verdant fields and the crystal clear breeze coursing through the air? Just taking one deep breath fills my spirit with inspiration like no muse ever could! I''m telling you, there is no place like Northwind in the entirety of the Eastern Kingdoms.', 'Can you feel the essence of this vale? The crimson trees, rolling verdant fields and the crystal clear breeze coursing through the air? Just taking one deep breath fills my spirit with inspiration like no muse ever could! I''m telling you, there is no place like Northwind in the entirety of the Eastern Kingdoms.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6229001, 'That foolish girl! This is the eleventh disaster caused by her I have to remedy. If she continues like that I will look like an old hag from all the stress it is causing me!', 'That foolish girl! This is the eleventh disaster caused by her I have to remedy. If she continues like that I will look like an old hag from all the stress it is causing me!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6229101, 'I''ve done it again. I won''t hear the end of it from the master for atleast a month. That''s what I get for trying my hands on difficult incantations on my own...', 'I''ve done it again. I won''t hear the end of it from the master for atleast a month. That''s what I get for trying my hands on difficult incantations on my own...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6229201, 'Sir Amberwood is a disgrace to the Northwind Guard. His predecessor would''ve never allowed Northwind to become this rundown.', 'Sir Amberwood is a disgrace to the Northwind Guard. His predecessor would''ve never allowed Northwind to become this rundown.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6229301, 'So much cruelty. This must be a test by the Light. Our faith has to remain strong during these hard times.', 'So much cruelty. This must be a test by the Light. Our faith has to remain strong during these hard times.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6229401, 'Why is father taking so long? He wanted to buy me these yummy donuts from the Jousting Grounds!', 'Why is father taking so long? He wanted to buy me these yummy donuts from the Jousting Grounds!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6229501, 'Interested in the newest publications from across the Eastern Kingdoms? From gnomish engineering dissertations to elaborate research on the human noble houses, you will surely find something to your liking.', 'Interested in the newest publications from across the Eastern Kingdoms? From gnomish engineering dissertations to elaborate research on the human noble houses, you will surely find something to your liking.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
