(6229701, 'I should focus on supporting Sister Argent with her educational duties, but the image of that burned abbey just can''t escape my mind.', 'I should focus on supporting Sister Argent with her educational duties, but the image of that burned abbey just can''t escape my mind.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
