(6230206, 'Hm, I''m not sure that''s what it was...', 'Hm, I''m not sure that''s what it was...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6230301, 'Arnor family.', 'Arnor family.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6230302, 'Grahan family.', 'Grahan family.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6230303, 'Prestor family.', 'Prestor family.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6230304, 'I took a small nap during last week''s school and missed who was very close to Duke Balor and Stormwind - can you remind me? I don''t want to disappoint Sister Argent.', 'I took a small nap during last week''s school and missed who was very close to Duke Balor and Stormwind - can you remind me? I don''t want to disappoint Sister Argent.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6230305, 'Hm, I''m not sure that''s what it was...', 'Hm, I''m not sure that''s what it was...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6230401, 'Mommy lies here. Daddy says that she is in a better place now, but I don''t understand that. Isn''t the best place here with us? I hope she comes back soon, so she can play with me and Joshua again!', 'Mommy lies here. Daddy says that she is in a better place now, but I don''t understand that. Isn''t the best place here with us? I hope she comes back soon, so she can play with me and Joshua again!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6230501, '<The boy isn''t saying anything and has a rather barren expression.>', '<The boy isn''t saying anything and has a rather barren expression.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6230701, 'Ready to test your aim? My arrows are the best in all of Northwind.', 'Ready to test your aim? My arrows are the best in all of Northwind.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6230801, 'I feel sullied by the stench of alcohol and misery of this place. Is this how the people of Stormwind pay reverence to the Light?', 'I feel sullied by the stench of alcohol and misery of this place. Is this how the people of Stormwind pay reverence to the Light?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6230901, 'Those pesky orcs are nothing but vermin. How dare they ruin my family''s house and plot like that? And why are my good-for-nothing sons such cowards?!', 'Those pesky orcs are nothing but vermin. How dare they ruin my family''s house and plot like that? And why are my good-for-nothing sons such cowards?!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6231001, 'Father has been broken from the stress of fulfilling the production quota for the nobility. Having our home overrun by these filthy orcs is just too much for him, I believe he lost it now altogther.', 'Father has been broken from the stress of fulfilling the production quota for the nobility. Having our home overrun by these filthy orcs is just too much for him, I believe he lost it now altogther.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6231101, 'Mother tries to hold the family together, but our bond was crumbling even before we lost our home. Best I can do is support her.', 'Mother tries to hold the family together, but our bond was crumbling even before we lost our home. Best I can do is support her.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6231201, 'We all are devastated by what happened, Mother and Father moreso than us, surely. Having their legacy be ransacked just like that after building it up over centuries? I can barely imagine the pain.', 'We all are devastated by what happened, Mother and Father moreso than us, surely. Having their legacy be ransacked just like that after building it up over centuries? I can barely imagine the pain.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6231301, 'My husband is in a terrible state, and my children are distraught at what has become of us. I, however, will not let this heavy mood stand any longer. We''ve built this with our own hands and hard work, and we will take it back with the same hands!', 'My husband is in a terrible state, and my children are distraught at what has become of us. I, however, will not let this heavy mood stand any longer. We''ve built this with our own hands and hard work, and we will take it back with the same hands!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6236701, 'We hail from Loch Modan with trading goods. It is a real pain to travel by boat from the Wetlands to Stormwind with cargo. Luckily, a friend in the Dwarven District loaned me this gypsy wagon to ensure the goods reach Ambershire. Sadly, he failed to mention its state of disrepair, so now I must wait for Gardim to fix it while also keeping an eye out for possible dangers. The merchant life has its ups and downs, I suppose.', 'We hail from Loch Modan with trading goods. It is a real pain to travel by boat from the Wetlands to Stormwind with cargo. Luckily, a friend in the Dwarven District loaned me this gypsy wagon to ensure the goods reach Ambershire. Sadly, he failed to mention its state of disrepair, so now I must wait for Gardim to fix it while also keeping an eye out for possible dangers. The merchant life has its ups and downs, I suppose.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6236801, 'Och! Being a bodyguard wasn''t enough for Thromli—now I have to be his handyman too. The bastard had better buy me a pint as soon as we reach Ambershire!', 'Och! Being a bodyguard wasn''t enough for Thromli—now I have to be his handyman too. The bastard had better buy me a pint as soon as we reach Ambershire!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6236901, '<This poor animal is unaccustomed to these lands; it is sweating profusely and seems burdened and tired.>', '<This poor animal is unaccustomed to these lands; it is sweating profusely and seems burdened and tired.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6237001, 'My sister and I met this traveling priestess just as we finished helping our kin in Darkshore. We have been a party of three ever since we boarded the boat to Stormwind. She seems quite adventurous, having just visited Alah''thalas before our fateful meeting. Yet, sadly, she cannot keep up with our stamina, which is understandable.', 'My sister and I met this traveling priestess just as we finished helping our kin in Darkshore. We have been a party of three ever since we boarded the boat to Stormwind. She seems quite adventurous, having just visited Alah''thalas before our fateful meeting. Yet, sadly, she cannot keep up with our stamina, which is understandable.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6237101, 'Olga is simply the funniest person I have ever met—so unlike my dull twin brother. Meeting her on our travels has been a blessing from Elune. I feel as though I have made a lifelong friend.', 'Olga is simply the funniest person I have ever met—so unlike my dull twin brother. Meeting her on our travels has been a blessing from Elune. I feel as though I have made a lifelong friend.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6237201, 'Ay, by the Light, these elves and their long legs! Bah, I need to be up on my feet—I''m here to see that winery! I must see for myself what had those elves in Alah''thalas so happy.', 'Ay, by the Light, these elves and their long legs! Bah, I need to be up on my feet—I''m here to see that winery! I must see for myself what had those elves in Alah''thalas so happy.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6237301, 'All these letters won''t deliver themselves! These guards had better let me go about my business sooner rather than later, right? I promised my dear wife, Tina, that I''d be home in time for our anniversary.', 'All these letters won''t deliver themselves! These guards had better let me go about my business sooner rather than later, right? I promised my dear wife, Tina, that I''d be home in time for our anniversary.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6237401, 'If only I could open this blasted lock! This is just like my father—gah! He hid away his "Alteraci legacy" in this damn chest, and my patience is running thin. How stubborn can an old mule be, denying his own son the only family heirloom he has...', 'If only I could open this blasted lock! This is just like my father—gah! He hid away his "Alteraci legacy" in this damn chest, and my patience is running thin. How stubborn can an old mule be, denying his own son the only family heirloom he has...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6237501, 'There''s barely anything worth reading on any of these bookshelves. I suppose they might have been if I hadn''t already read every single one of them at least twice...', 'There''s barely anything worth reading on any of these bookshelves. I suppose they might have been if I hadn''t already read every single one of them at least twice...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6237601, 'I had hoped this would be the best place to retire, yet once more I am denied peace of mind. You see, I worry a great deal—it must be because of that time we had to lock ourselves in Ironforge, praying that no orc would ransack our home. I am a simple man; I''ve never raised arms in all my years, and I fear what the days to come may bring.', 'I had hoped this would be the best place to retire, yet once more I am denied peace of mind. You see, I worry a great deal—it must be because of that time we had to lock ourselves in Ironforge, praying that no orc would ransack our home. I am a simple man; I''ve never raised arms in all my years, and I fear what the days to come may bring.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6237701, 'New around here, are you? I hope you won''t be causing any trouble. Otherwise, you''ll have to face me. People call me Brick—I might not look like much, but my head is as strong as a piece of obsidian. So unless your chin wishes to meet my forehead, I''d suggest you stay clear of trouble.', 'New around here, are you? I hope you won''t be causing any trouble. Otherwise, you''ll have to face me. People call me Brick—I might not look like much, but my head is as strong as a piece of obsidian. So unless your chin wishes to meet my forehead, I''d suggest you stay clear of trouble.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6237801, '<Snores loudly.>', '<Snores loudly.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6237901, 'I enjoy looking at the town from my chair. Each day, I would see children playing in the leaf piles, happily dancing around. Nowadays, we''ve been robbed of that kind of peace. Children are missing or kept inside by paranoid parents. Were I five years younger, I would take my sword and show this young generation what must be done at times like this! Yet, I am cursed with weak legs and a lazy bum of a son—he''s probably asleep right now. At least the Light blessed me with better daughters', 'I enjoy looking at the town from my chair. Each day, I would see children playing in the leaf piles, happily dancing around. Nowadays, we''ve been robbed of that kind of peace. Children are missing or kept inside by paranoid parents. Were I five years younger, I would take my sword and show this young generation what must be done at times like this! Yet, I am cursed with weak legs and a lazy bum of a son—he''s probably asleep right now. At least the Light blessed me with better daughters', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6238101, 'Doomed to stack hay while my brother ran away from home to become a big-shot hunter, hidden behind the safe walls of Stormwind. I wonder what he''s even hunting—rats or the beasts crawling in the sewers? I miss that fool.', 'Doomed to stack hay while my brother ran away from home to become a big-shot hunter, hidden behind the safe walls of Stormwind. I wonder what he''s even hunting—rats or the beasts crawling in the sewers? I miss that fool.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6238201, 'I''m afraid all alcohol sales outside of inns, taverns, or the jousting grounds have been halted during the tournament, as Lord Amberwood wishes to avoid wandering drunks that may cause altercations during such events. If you wish to buy any of my crafts, you''ll have to do so another day.', 'I''m afraid all alcohol sales outside of inns, taverns, or the jousting grounds have been halted during the tournament, as Lord Amberwood wishes to avoid wandering drunks that may cause altercations during such events. If you wish to buy any of my crafts, you''ll have to do so another day.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6238301, 'Anu belore dela''na. Tensions rise within the kingdom. People are scared, uneasy and doubtful. Those doubts cloud their hearts, and open the gates for mistrust. In times like these, heroes of old can bring us solace, was it not their faith in others that laid the foundation for us people to prosper on.$B$BIt is my solemn duty to hold vigil over this altar, honoring the heroes who would pose a shining example to us all. I will not forsake it, no matter the cost.', 'Anu belore dela''na. Tensions rise within the kingdom. People are scared, uneasy and doubtful. Those doubts cloud their hearts, and open the gates for mistrust. In times like these, heroes of old can bring us solace, was it not their faith in others that laid the foundation for us people to prosper on.$B$BIt is my solemn duty to hold vigil over this altar, honoring the heroes who would pose a shining example to us all. I will not forsake it, no matter the cost.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6238401, 'Psst! Be quiet! I am hiding from Brick and you talking to a pile of leaves isn''t exactly helping me stay undetected. Now shoo, before his walnut brain is connecting the dots!', 'Psst! Be quiet! I am hiding from Brick and you talking to a pile of leaves isn''t exactly helping me stay undetected. Now shoo, before his walnut brain is connecting the dots!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6238601, 'It is getting more difficult to keep the roadways clear each day. The Dragonmaw Orcs may have been pushed back for now, but it is only a matter of time before they return.$B$BI pray that we have the strength to repel them again when the time comes.', 'It is getting more difficult to keep the roadways clear each day. The Dragonmaw Orcs may have been pushed back for now, but it is only a matter of time before they return.$B$BI pray that we have the strength to repel them again when the time comes.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6238801, 'What brings you to Grim Reaches? If it is sight seeing then I got some bad news. The only thing you are going to see is the presence of Dragonmaw orcs that lurk throughout the countryside.', 'What brings you to Grim Reaches? If it is sight seeing then I got some bad news. The only thing you are going to see is the presence of Dragonmaw orcs that lurk throughout the countryside.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6238901, 'It is my duty to keep tabs upon the populace, and make sure to keep a steady count of how many live within our confines. I keep track of how many live here, and who lives where.$B$B As Clerk of Dun Kithas, I  also oversee documenting and filing issues with the council itself. If you have any concerns, or suggestions for Dun Kithas, let me know, and I can pass it on to the Council itself.', 'It is my duty to keep tabs upon the populace, and make sure to keep a steady count of how many live within our confines. I keep track of how many live here, and who lives where.$B$B As Clerk of Dun Kithas, I  also oversee documenting and filing issues with the council itself. If you have any concerns, or suggestions for Dun Kithas, let me know, and I can pass it on to the Council itself.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239001, 'The history of this region is steeped in tradition, conflict, and prosperity. The Grim Reaches was once a fertile and suitable land for many of the families and nobles that once lived within the great halls of Grim Batol itself!$B$BOurs is a weathered story, and one of hardship. We have endured, and adapted to face the threats that have continually sought our destruction. Many of those threats are long gone, and yet we still remain, a testament to the willpower of dwarves within Grim Reaches.', 'The history of this region is steeped in tradition, conflict, and prosperity. The Grim Reaches was once a fertile and suitable land for many of the families and nobles that once lived within the great halls of Grim Batol itself!$B$BOurs is a weathered story, and one of hardship. We have endured, and adapted to face the threats that have continually sought our destruction. Many of those threats are long gone, and yet we still remain, a testament to the willpower of dwarves within Grim Reaches.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239101, 'Tell me more about the fall of Stolgaz Keep.', 'Tell me more about the fall of Stolgaz Keep.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239102, 'Tell me more about Baggoth.', 'Tell me more about Baggoth.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239103, 'A fellow historian perhaps? Are you here to learn of the great Baggoth Ironmantle? Renowned general and architect of the Grim Reaches? Did you know it was Baggoth himself that helped orchestrate the defense of the first Dragonmaw incursion?$B$B...Maybe you''re more interested in the fall of Stolgaz Keep some years ago?', 'A fellow historian perhaps? Are you here to learn of the great Baggoth Ironmantle? Renowned general and architect of the Grim Reaches? Did you know it was Baggoth himself that helped orchestrate the defense of the first Dragonmaw incursion?$B$B...Maybe you''re more interested in the fall of Stolgaz Keep some years ago?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239104, 'Stolgaz Keep''s destruction lives in the hearts of many dwarves within the Grim Reaches. It is a tale of woe, and one that we tell often to not forget.$B$B Stolgaz Keep was created some eighty years ago, and used as a fortress to defend the region from any threats that the Grim Reaches could face. It was a place that many often visited to taste its more famous ''Stolgaz Ale'', a traditional beverage with a sweet and textured flavor!$B$B A few years ago, the Dragonmaw orcs returned, and with them came conflict. Their efforts focused heavily on Stolgaz Keep, eventually bringing it, and its brave defenders into ruin. Many attempts were made to retake it through the years. Though some of them had made progress, all of them ended in failure. The land is littered in destruction, and now occupied permanently by the Dragonmaw... I would advise avoiding the roads that lead north.', 'Stolgaz Keep''s destruction lives in the hearts of many dwarves within the Grim Reaches. It is a tale of woe, and one that we tell often to not forget.$B$B Stolgaz Keep was created some eighty years ago, and used as a fortress to defend the region from any threats that the Grim Reaches could face. It was a place that many often visited to taste its more famous ''Stolgaz Ale'', a traditional beverage with a sweet and textured flavor!$B$B A few years ago, the Dragonmaw orcs returned, and with them came conflict. Their efforts focused heavily on Stolgaz Keep, eventually bringing it, and its brave defenders into ruin. Many attempts were made to retake it through the years. Though some of them had made progress, all of them ended in failure. The land is littered in destruction, and now occupied permanently by the Dragonmaw... I would advise avoiding the roads that lead north.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239201, 'Welcome, and make yourself at home. Dun Kithas is known for its hospitality!', 'Welcome, and make yourself at home. Dun Kithas is known for its hospitality!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239301, 'I am Keeper Blackforge, responsible with keeping the records of Dun Kithas. It is my duty to record what takes place to who, and where. Should anybody steal, or speak ill of another, it is written and recorded by myself...$B$BI would advise keeping the peace, the last thing you want is to end up within the records of Dun Kithas.', 'I am Keeper Blackforge, responsible with keeping the records of Dun Kithas. It is my duty to record what takes place to who, and where. Should anybody steal, or speak ill of another, it is written and recorded by myself...$B$BI would advise keeping the peace, the last thing you want is to end up within the records of Dun Kithas.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239401, 'What is it that you want, can''t you see that we''re busy with important work here? I can''t waste my time with nosey adventurers from beyond our borders. There are more pressing matters that need attention.', 'What is it that you want, can''t you see that we''re busy with important work here? I can''t waste my time with nosey adventurers from beyond our borders. There are more pressing matters that need attention.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239501, 'Welcome to Dun Kithas, I am Magistrate Hurdam Toughhand, I was elected as the head of governance here to work with my fellow councilors in deciding what should, and should not be done. These decisions hold extreme weight in how we deal with many things, from the mundane, to the more serious. If you have an issue that may need resolving, or a concern that should be brought to the council, please speak with Enumerator Gravelcrest upstairs. He should give you the proper documents to file any grievances, concerns, or suggestions to be brought up in our next meeting.$B$B Oh, and do not mind Dandegg, he has a bit of a short temper, and does not appreciate the perspective of outsiders.', 'Welcome to Dun Kithas, I am Magistrate Hurdam Toughhand, I was elected as the head of governance here to work with my fellow councilors in deciding what should, and should not be done. These decisions hold extreme weight in how we deal with many things, from the mundane, to the more serious. If you have an issue that may need resolving, or a concern that should be brought to the council, please speak with Enumerator Gravelcrest upstairs. He should give you the proper documents to file any grievances, concerns, or suggestions to be brought up in our next meeting.$B$B Oh, and do not mind Dandegg, he has a bit of a short temper, and does not appreciate the perspective of outsiders.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239601, 'If we are to ever have peace for our people than our actions must be decisive! The orcs have spent far too long within the Grim Reaches and it is about time they are expelled.', 'If we are to ever have peace for our people than our actions must be decisive! The orcs have spent far too long within the Grim Reaches and it is about time they are expelled.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239701, 'A darkness has begun to creep into the Grim Reaches. My defenders are stretched thin and we are beset by enemies on all sides. While I was commanding the defense of Baggoth''s Wall the lands themselves have begun to be overrun by ghost and mongrel alike. I do hope you''re here to assist, we could use any help we can get.', 'A darkness has begun to creep into the Grim Reaches. My defenders are stretched thin and we are beset by enemies on all sides. While I was commanding the defense of Baggoth''s Wall the lands themselves have begun to be overrun by ghost and mongrel alike. I do hope you''re here to assist, we could use any help we can get.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6239901, 'Is there something that I can assist you with outsider?', 'Is there something that I can assist you with outsider?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6240001, 'Greetings, and welcome adventurer! It is my duty to bring the latest news of the world to the citizens of Dun Kithas, and to announce the will of our great council.', 'Greetings, and welcome adventurer! It is my duty to bring the latest news of the world to the citizens of Dun Kithas, and to announce the will of our great council.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6240501, 'Those blasted... All of that work, gone in an instant$B$B<Groldan continues to grumble incoherently.>', 'Those blasted... All of that work, gone in an instant$B$B<Groldan continues to grumble incoherently.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6240601, 'We were on track to uncovering some great marvels up at the excavation.', 'We were on track to uncovering some great marvels up at the excavation.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6240701, 'I came here to discover relics of the past, and now we''re stuck here waiting around to hear more news from the Explorer''s League.', 'I came here to discover relics of the past, and now we''re stuck here waiting around to hear more news from the Explorer''s League.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6241101, 'I warned them that the troggs would be an issue, but no one wants to listen to old Kegg and his cooky nonsense.$B$B<Kegg lets out a maniacal laugh.>', 'I warned them that the troggs would be an issue, but no one wants to listen to old Kegg and his cooky nonsense.$B$B<Kegg lets out a maniacal laugh.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6241201, 'I''ve come all the way from Ironforge, my family is interested in some of the local traditions here in Dun Kithas.', 'I''ve come all the way from Ironforge, my family is interested in some of the local traditions here in Dun Kithas.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6241401, 'The Grim Reaches are one of the most resource rich locations on Azeroth. I have spent most of my life looking for a rare gemstone and I think it may lie just beneath the hills here.', 'The Grim Reaches are one of the most resource rich locations on Azeroth. I have spent most of my life looking for a rare gemstone and I think it may lie just beneath the hills here.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6241701, 'If you need any blacksmithing work, you can talk to Margella...', 'If you need any blacksmithing work, you can talk to Margella...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6241801, 'If you need any blacksmithing work, you can talk to Ragdan...', 'If you need any blacksmithing work, you can talk to Ragdan...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
