(6242201, 'Why hello there adventurer, we''re much alike, out trying to save the world from the dark, evil, and scary things no? Perhaps I''m just assuming but you look like the kind of person that offers assistance to those in need.$B$B I must admit, that''s an admirable trait, one that we both have. We certainly are nice people.', 'Why hello there adventurer, we''re much alike, out trying to save the world from the dark, evil, and scary things no? Perhaps I''m just assuming but you look like the kind of person that offers assistance to those in need.$B$B I must admit, that''s an admirable trait, one that we both have. We certainly are nice people.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6242301, 'Dorthas is known to ramble on, I just nod my head until he gets to the point.', 'Dorthas is known to ramble on, I just nod my head until he gets to the point.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6242501, 'Watch yourself here, I won''t tolerate anyone causing trouble.', 'Watch yourself here, I won''t tolerate anyone causing trouble.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6242601, 'This land is scarred by battle, weakened by the conflict. Perhaps this is time for the Horde to place its claim.', 'This land is scarred by battle, weakened by the conflict. Perhaps this is time for the Horde to place its claim.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6242801, 'A strong orc can change the fate of any battle, the might of a powerful warrior can change history itself.', 'A strong orc can change the fate of any battle, the might of a powerful warrior can change history itself.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6242901, 'You looking for a good cut of meat? I''m making due with what I have, but I''m sure I can satisfy your desires.', 'You looking for a good cut of meat? I''m making due with what I have, but I''m sure I can satisfy your desires.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6243101, 'Blasted, shoddy work. Our siege machines are crude and out dated, this design of catapult could be severely improved. If we are to ever make our place in Grim Reaches we will need vastly superior equipment and machinery to facilitate capable assaults.$B$B I''m going to have to work overtime if they expect me to do anything substantial. I don''t suspect we can go back to the old horde mantra of - "Throw more orcs at the problem". We''re lacking manpower as it is.', 'Blasted, shoddy work. Our siege machines are crude and out dated, this design of catapult could be severely improved. If we are to ever make our place in Grim Reaches we will need vastly superior equipment and machinery to facilitate capable assaults.$B$B I''m going to have to work overtime if they expect me to do anything substantial. I don''t suspect we can go back to the old horde mantra of - "Throw more orcs at the problem". We''re lacking manpower as it is.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6243301, 'Welcome adventurer, it is good to see more eager blood travel to the fringes in search of glory. I am commander of this base, and I enact the Warchief''s will upon the land. If we are to truly make this land our own than we must be prepared for the conflict ahead.', 'Welcome adventurer, it is good to see more eager blood travel to the fringes in search of glory. I am commander of this base, and I enact the Warchief''s will upon the land. If we are to truly make this land our own than we must be prepared for the conflict ahead.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6243401, 'I am Ranagg, advisor to Aggnash. It is always good to have support, even in such foreign lands.$B$B Do you bring word from Orgrimmar?', 'I am Ranagg, advisor to Aggnash. It is always good to have support, even in such foreign lands.$B$B Do you bring word from Orgrimmar?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6243501, 'Even in foreign lands as these, warriors need a place to rest their head and replenish their strength.', 'Even in foreign lands as these, warriors need a place to rest their head and replenish their strength.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244301, 'Pet Cheese Wizard.', 'Pet Cheese Wizard.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244302, '<Cheese Wizard stares blankly at Magilou, judging her every move.>', '<Cheese Wizard stares blankly at Magilou, judging her every move.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244303, '<Cheese Wizard meows at you with a frustrated tone. Maybe you should not have touched the hat.>', '<Cheese Wizard meows at you with a frustrated tone. Maybe you should not have touched the hat.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244401, '<Pet Bobby Joe.>', '<Pet Bobby Joe.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244402, '<Bobby Joe sleeps comfortably under the shade of the tree.>', '<Bobby Joe sleeps comfortably under the shade of the tree.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244403, '<Bobby Joe stretches and purrs at your touch. He seeks the palm of your hand with his head, asking for more head pats.>', '<Bobby Joe stretches and purrs at your touch. He seeks the palm of your hand with his head, asking for more head pats.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244501, 'Pet Misty.', 'Pet Misty.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244502, '<Misty stares deeply into your eyes.>', '<Misty stares deeply into your eyes.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244503, '<Misty purrs and playfully bites at your fingers.>', '<Misty purrs and playfully bites at your fingers.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244601, 'Pet Monkey.', 'Pet Monkey.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244602, '<Monkey zooms around in a circle from pile to pile.>', '<Monkey zooms around in a circle from pile to pile.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244603, '<Monkey zooms right into you, making you fall on the ground. He keeps brushing his fur onto your torso, from left to right.>', '<Monkey zooms right into you, making you fall on the ground. He keeps brushing his fur onto your torso, from left to right.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244801, 'Me and Betty are playing hide and seek. She never finds me in time for dinner though.', 'Me and Betty are playing hide and seek. She never finds me in time for dinner though.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6244901, 'Jeremy is a big meanie. I can never find his stupid hiding place but he still always wants to play this game. All I want to do is play house...', 'Jeremy is a big meanie. I can never find his stupid hiding place but he still always wants to play this game. All I want to do is play house...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6245501, 'For me, Balor was nothing more than a mare my parents used to jokingly scare me with; to prepare me for the dangers outside of Stormwind. I even continued telling the same terrifying fairy tales to my children, much to the dismay of my husband. Now that I am here, I wish those stories were reality.', 'For me, Balor was nothing more than a mare my parents used to jokingly scare me with; to prepare me for the dangers outside of Stormwind. I even continued telling the same terrifying fairy tales to my children, much to the dismay of my husband. Now that I am here, I wish those stories were reality.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6245701, 'New around here? This place is in a league of its own, even for someone as experienced as me. Keep your wits about you and stay alert; you never know what waits around the next corner!', 'New around here? This place is in a league of its own, even for someone as experienced as me. Keep your wits about you and stay alert; you never know what waits around the next corner!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6245801, 'Greetings! My name is Noppsy Spickerspan and I am responsible for archiving everything that occurs during this operation. Balor has a rich history, with many mysteries still left unanswered ever since Stormwind lost it in the First War. If you discover any documents or similar records, don''t hesitate to bring them to me.', 'Greetings! My name is Noppsy Spickerspan and I am responsible for archiving everything that occurs during this operation. Balor has a rich history, with many mysteries still left unanswered ever since Stormwind lost it in the First War. If you discover any documents or similar records, don''t hesitate to bring them to me.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6246301, 'This humid air is like poison to my beautiful weapons!', 'This humid air is like poison to my beautiful weapons!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6246601, 'Where are all the servants? I''ve been waiting for my strawberry parfait for over three hours now. Whoever is taking their sweet time with my dessert will have their last day under my brother''s employment!', 'Where are all the servants? I''ve been waiting for my strawberry parfait for over three hours now. Whoever is taking their sweet time with my dessert will have their last day under my brother''s employment!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6246701, 'Ruin. Devastation. Death. Nothing more to find on this once luscious island. I remember the verdant trees and hills, the sweet and salty breeze coursing over the mountains and the warm rays of the sun on my skin. None of it remains. Regret and misery is all you can see.', 'Ruin. Devastation. Death. Nothing more to find on this once luscious island. I remember the verdant trees and hills, the sweet and salty breeze coursing over the mountains and the warm rays of the sun on my skin. None of it remains. Regret and misery is all you can see.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6246801, 'Just what are the girls thinking? Repairing a zeppelin with constant rain and humidity you can only find in a goblin sauna? I don''t know if that speaks for their trust in my abilities or their loss of sanity.', 'Just what are the girls thinking? Repairing a zeppelin with constant rain and humidity you can only find in a goblin sauna? I don''t know if that speaks for their trust in my abilities or their loss of sanity.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6247001, 'Aye, this place is brimming with history, ready for the taking! These old farts from the Explorer''s League will have the most dumbfounded look when I return with a monumental discovery!', 'Aye, this place is brimming with history, ready for the taking! These old farts from the Explorer''s League will have the most dumbfounded look when I return with a monumental discovery!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6247101, 'This island is ailing, a sickness germinates within and it is aching to burst free. Just what is my Shan''do looking for in this accursed place?', 'This island is ailing, a sickness germinates within and it is aching to burst free. Just what is my Shan''do looking for in this accursed place?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6247201, 'It''s been ages since my brother and I were last in Stormwind. We haven''t left Theramore since departing from Lordaeron, so this reunion feels bittersweet to me. Still, I cannot let this hold me back in the tournament.', 'It''s been ages since my brother and I were last in Stormwind. We haven''t left Theramore since departing from Lordaeron, so this reunion feels bittersweet to me. Still, I cannot let this hold me back in the tournament.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6247301, 'Alessa tries to put up a brave face, but I can see she has trouble keeping up the facade. Our family hails from Stormwind and fled to Lordaeron after the First War, so I can only imagine what races through her mind.', 'Alessa tries to put up a brave face, but I can see she has trouble keeping up the facade. Our family hails from Stormwind and fled to Lordaeron after the First War, so I can only imagine what races through her mind.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6247401, 'Lady Proudmoore chose me and the Farwind siblings as representatives of our port city. She wishes to foster relations not only with Stormwind, but the other human nations as well. An admirable goal, and I will not allow her ambitions to fail.', 'Lady Proudmoore chose me and the Farwind siblings as representatives of our port city. She wishes to foster relations not only with Stormwind, but the other human nations as well. An admirable goal, and I will not allow her ambitions to fail.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6247501, 'One can only muse at the thought of holding a tournament during these times. What on earth are these Stormwindians thinking? Do they not see what transpires right in front of their doorstep?', 'One can only muse at the thought of holding a tournament during these times. What on earth are these Stormwindians thinking? Do they not see what transpires right in front of their doorstep?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6247601, 'My family has a small, unremarkable farm in the outskirts of Stromgarde, yet here I am. I am honored to have been chosen as a representative of our kingdom; I will make them proud no matter what!', 'My family has a small, unremarkable farm in the outskirts of Stromgarde, yet here I am. I am honored to have been chosen as a representative of our kingdom; I will make them proud no matter what!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6247701, 'Just standing here gives me the shivers. I''d rather return to Stromgarde and assist my brethren, but diplomacy calls me to participate in… this.', 'Just standing here gives me the shivers. I''d rather return to Stromgarde and assist my brethren, but diplomacy calls me to participate in… this.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6247801, 'Being forced to participate in this idiotic tournament is a disgrace to any truthful Kul Tiran. What do these traitorous bastards think this will accomplish?!', 'Being forced to participate in this idiotic tournament is a disgrace to any truthful Kul Tiran. What do these traitorous bastards think this will accomplish?!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6248101, 'These youngins underestimate a man of my age far too easily. Just you wait, I will show them just what Dalarani wits look like!', 'These youngins underestimate a man of my age far too easily. Just you wait, I will show them just what Dalarani wits look like!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6248201, 'My master is a passionate man, rarely have I seen someone as proud of Dalaran as him! With him participating at the joust, there is no way we will lose the tournament!', 'My master is a passionate man, rarely have I seen someone as proud of Dalaran as him! With him participating at the joust, there is no way we will lose the tournament!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6248301, 'Have you seen that silver fox from Stromgarde over there? Isn''t he just stunning?$B$B<Modera''s eyes are sparkling at the sight of Commander Leder. Being obviously enchanted by his appearance, she loses her train of thought before quickly regaining composure.>$B$BOh, excuse me. How rude. I am Caitlyn Modera, daughter of Archmage Modera of the Council of Six governing Dalaran. My mother is incredibly busy rebuilding our great city, as you may have heard already, so I am here in her stead representing Dalaran.', 'Have you seen that silver fox from Stromgarde over there? Isn''t he just stunning?$B$B<Modera''s eyes are sparkling at the sight of Commander Leder. Being obviously enchanted by his appearance, she loses her train of thought before quickly regaining composure.>$B$BOh, excuse me. How rude. I am Caitlyn Modera, daughter of Archmage Modera of the Council of Six governing Dalaran. My mother is incredibly busy rebuilding our great city, as you may have heard already, so I am here in her stead representing Dalaran.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6248401, 'First Redridge and now Northwind? Do these orcs not know their place?', 'First Redridge and now Northwind? Do these orcs not know their place?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6248501, '<You are met with an icecold glare, and feel definitely not welcome here.>', '<You are met with an icecold glare, and feel definitely not welcome here.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6248801, 'I am unsure if sending me on my own here is a sign of Master Shaw''s trust in my abilities; or some sort of twisted punishment.', 'I am unsure if sending me on my own here is a sign of Master Shaw''s trust in my abilities; or some sort of twisted punishment.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6248901, 'I am here on behalf of SI:7 Operative Hawthorne. Have you noticed anything suspicious during the previous nights?', 'I am here on behalf of SI:7 Operative Hawthorne. Have you noticed anything suspicious during the previous nights?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6248902, 'It is all my fault! If I hadn''t gone to Stormwind alone and took them with me, they... they...! Our house; rummaged and broken into, it must''ve been terrifying for them! Oh, good $C, please, I beg of you! Bring back my dear babies, they must be scared and tired and... By the Light, I cannot take this much longer!$B$B<Judith is breaking down in tears.>', 'It is all my fault! If I hadn''t gone to Stormwind alone and took them with me, they... they...! Our house; rummaged and broken into, it must''ve been terrifying for them! Oh, good $C, please, I beg of you! Bring back my dear babies, they must be scared and tired and... By the Light, I cannot take this much longer!$B$B<Judith is breaking down in tears.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6248903, '<The woman is shaking and distressed.>', '<The woman is shaking and distressed.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6249001, 'The young woman lies motionless on the ground. Her skin is cold to the touch and any life has long left her body.', 'The young woman lies motionless on the ground. Her skin is cold to the touch and any life has long left her body.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6249201, '<Inspect the corpse.>', '<Inspect the corpse.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6249202, 'This man is heavily mutilated. Stab wounds and twisted limbs make him almost unrecognizable.', 'This man is heavily mutilated. Stab wounds and twisted limbs make him almost unrecognizable.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6249301, 'The duck is breathing heavily and seems to have injured its left wing.', 'The duck is breathing heavily and seems to have injured its left wing.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6249401, 'Sounds like you''re in need of some assistance.', 'Sounds like you''re in need of some assistance.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6249402, 'I regret every single minute of my precious time I''m still spending in this dump! My entourage and I traveled here from my estate in Stormwind past all the horrible dangers in the woods. My goal was to gain influence with his Lordship and acquire a semi-serious footing in the wealthy lands of Northwind. But now my custom fashioned purse with my sigil ring had been stolen from me, even though I had it on me at all times! To think someone put his revolting fingers on me makes me want to puke.', 'I regret every single minute of my precious time I''m still spending in this dump! My entourage and I traveled here from my estate in Stormwind past all the horrible dangers in the woods. My goal was to gain influence with his Lordship and acquire a semi-serious footing in the wealthy lands of Northwind. But now my custom fashioned purse with my sigil ring had been stolen from me, even though I had it on me at all times! To think someone put his revolting fingers on me makes me want to puke.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6249403, 'I hate how right you are, peasant. This letter here is all I have for clues. I found it instead of my purse in my belongings. Take it and use it to bring me back my purse, now!', 'I hate how right you are, peasant. This letter here is all I have for clues. I found it instead of my purse in my belongings. Take it and use it to bring me back my purse, now!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6249801, 'I challenge you to combat.', 'I challenge you to combat.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6249802, '<Razjal gives you a hostile gaze.>', '<Razjal gives you a hostile gaze.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6251301, 'My wife and I scraped all our belongings together, trying to settle here in Northwind. If only we had known how horrible the situation truly is. I''ve no doubt Lord Amberwood is a kind-hearted man, yet I dread the outcome if he declines our humble offering for a short stay in his keep.', 'My wife and I scraped all our belongings together, trying to settle here in Northwind. If only we had known how horrible the situation truly is. I''ve no doubt Lord Amberwood is a kind-hearted man, yet I dread the outcome if he declines our humble offering for a short stay in his keep.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6251401, 'Many of our kind joined the expedition to Alah''thalas and have rebuilt that ancient relic. Not us, though. We cannot bear to live in the shadows of our past, clinging to it like a snotty child begging its mother for forgiveness. For us, a new path lies ahead... far away from the horrors we''ve had to endure.', 'Many of our kind joined the expedition to Alah''thalas and have rebuilt that ancient relic. Not us, though. We cannot bear to live in the shadows of our past, clinging to it like a snotty child begging its mother for forgiveness. For us, a new path lies ahead... far away from the horrors we''ve had to endure.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6251501, 'By the Light, my patience runs dry. Is this kingdom suddenly plagued by complete incompetence?!', 'By the Light, my patience runs dry. Is this kingdom suddenly plagued by complete incompetence?!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6251601, 'This is just grand. First we trek all the way through these barely protected streets and now we have to wait for an audience with the lord? In all the years we''ve been travelling to Northwind, this has never happened before. Simply appalling!', 'This is just grand. First we trek all the way through these barely protected streets and now we have to wait for an audience with the lord? In all the years we''ve been travelling to Northwind, this has never happened before. Simply appalling!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6251801, '<Ruffle Bristlebelly over his round tummy.>', '<Ruffle Bristlebelly over his round tummy.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6251802, '<The boar is snoring loudly.>', '<The boar is snoring loudly.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6251803, '<Bristlebelly enjoys the scratches thoroughly and rolls around in the warm leaves.>', '<Bristlebelly enjoys the scratches thoroughly and rolls around in the warm leaves.>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6251901, 'If you think this place is scary - ha! You''re in for a ride whenever you''re entering the Undermine slums. This island is nothing compared to that hellhole.', 'If you think this place is scary - ha! You''re in for a ride whenever you''re entering the Undermine slums. This island is nothing compared to that hellhole.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6252001, 'Yunie beats herself over for us being stranded here. She should spend her energy on putting the blame on Verix and getting her compass back. I like her much more when she is taking action instead of moping around.', 'Yunie beats herself over for us being stranded here. She should spend her energy on putting the blame on Verix and getting her compass back. I like her much more when she is taking action instead of moping around.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6252101, 'This was supposed to be another routine cargo delivery, just like any other before. But no, this brainiac of a goblin Verix just had to change course for a ‘shortcut'' that would save us tons of fuel. Too bad this shortcut turned out to be directly above an island cursed by a never-ending thunderstorm, which promptly struck our zeppelin, stranding us here! We''ve been fighting for our survival for two weeks now and morale started to dwindle. Yet having you stand before me must be Lady Luck''s way of rewarding our perseverance.', 'This was supposed to be another routine cargo delivery, just like any other before. But no, this brainiac of a goblin Verix just had to change course for a ‘shortcut'' that would save us tons of fuel. Too bad this shortcut turned out to be directly above an island cursed by a never-ending thunderstorm, which promptly struck our zeppelin, stranding us here! We''ve been fighting for our survival for two weeks now and morale started to dwindle. Yet having you stand before me must be Lady Luck''s way of rewarding our perseverance.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(6255401, 'Fleshy?', 'Fleshy?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
